{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhhf1v1uqvk0","created":1775005825299,"text":"电饭煲"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgypb5a7u4g0","created":1773105124772,"text":"低糖饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0n30xio3k0","created":1773301966077,"text":"煮饭--P10引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃时，经P9脚反馈后，P10引脚高电平持续4min","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0omz3i7gg0","created":1773306350479,"text":"焖饭--P10引脚高电平15s，低电平25s--27次，时长18min\n当NTC检测103℃，经P9脚反馈，P10引脚低电平--继电器断开停止加热","layout":null,"priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0orzmnduo0","created":1773306743457,"text":"保温：65-70℃\nNTC检测温度低于65℃时，P10引脚高电平10s，低电平20s--间歇加热\n高于70℃时，P10引脚低电平--停止加热\n循环","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb63g16w0","created":1773105126539,"text":"柴火饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kitrnm600","created":1773802540765,"text":"预热--P10高电平15s，低电平25s--时长2min；\nP10引脚高电平10s，低电平30s；\n当NTC检测60℃，经P9脚反馈，P10引脚高电平--持续加热","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kmzk0hso0","created":1773802866821,"text":"煮沸--当NTC检测100℃，经P9脚反馈，P10引脚高电平20s，低电平20s；","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5ko9blmso0","created":1773802966444,"text":"出锅巴--当NTC检测102℃，经P9脚反馈，P10引脚高电平25s，低电平15s--开关2次；\nP10引脚高电平32s，低电平8s--循环\n当NTC检测140℃，P15引脚低电平12min（倒计时）","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kusi71xs0","created":1773803478387,"text":"保温","priority":4,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb6hc6x40","created":1773105127379,"text":"杂粮饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5j5ij90pc0","created":1773798676469,"text":"煮饭--P10引脚高电平--继电器启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，经P9脚反馈，P10引脚高电平32s，低电平8s\n循环","priority":1,"expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5j6fjbwc80","created":1773798748307,"text":"焖饭：\n当NTC检测103℃，P10引脚高电平13s，低电平280s；\nP10引脚高电平15s，低电平25s；高电平32s，低电平8s；\n高电平15s，低电平20min（倒计时）","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5j93kxs6o0","created":1773798957376,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb6zl6e00","created":1773105128483,"text":"香浓粥","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ov2z7sdc0","created":1773306985840,"text":"煮沸--P10引脚高电平--继电器启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，经P9脚反馈，P15引脚高电平持续1min","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0owqc24io0","created":1773307115047,"text":"熬粥\nP15引脚高电平10s，低电平48s--开关60次，时长58min；","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oxl5bc800","created":1773307182119,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypbcbym3c0","created":1773105140115,"text":"美味汤","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ov2z7sdc0","created":1773306985840,"text":"煮沸--P15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，P15引脚高电平持续5min","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0owqc24io0","created":1773307115047,"text":"煲汤\n①P15引脚低电平持续3min，高电平持续2min；\n②P15引脚高电平15s，低电平25s--开关90次，时长1h","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oxl5bc800","created":1773307182119,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypbcq95pc0","created":1773105140979,"text":"火锅","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ov2z7sdc0","created":1773306985840,"text":"煮沸--P15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，继电器通断依档位切换","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0owqc24io0","created":1773307115047,"text":"6档：P15引脚持续高电平\n5档：P15引脚高电平30s，低电平10s；\n4档：P15引脚高电平20s，低电平20s；\n3档：P15引脚高电平15s，低电平25s；\n2档：P15引脚高电平10s，低电平30s；\n1档：P15引脚高电平6s，低电平34s；","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypbd3hhfs0","created":1773105141779,"text":"蒸煮","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1glqykhnk0","created":1773385245479,"text":"煮沸--P15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1goyf290g0","created":1773385496807,"text":"①当NTC检测100℃，P15引脚高电平持续15min；\n②当NTC检测温度高于125℃，P15引脚低电平并触发蜂鸣器报警--继电器断开停止加热","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1gqaga1go0","created":1773385601366,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypbdgpz2o0","created":1773105142579,"text":"焖炖","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1gr9z0pl40","created":1773385678686,"text":"煮沸--P15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，P15引脚电平转换--继电器动作","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1gsdcvrr40","created":1773385764419,"text":"焖炖\nP15引脚高电平10s，低电平30s--开关45次，30min","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1gu6mxwkg0","created":1773385906518,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyq6f4zcj40","created":1773107575512,"text":"温泉蛋","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1guas5t0g0","created":1773385915541,"text":"加热--P15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测65℃，P15引脚电平转换，继电器动作","priority":1,"expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1h0oyv6yg0","created":1773386416606,"text":"缓慢加热\nP15引脚高电平10s，低电平30s\n当NTC引脚检测70℃，P15引脚低电平--继电器断开停止加热","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1h6vh0snc0","created":1773386900950,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyq6fs00js0","created":1773107576904,"text":"保温","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0orzmnduo0","created":1773306743457,"text":"保温：65-70℃\nNTC检测温度低于65℃时，P15引脚高电平10s，低电平20s--间歇加热\n高于70℃时，P15引脚低电平--停止加热\n循环","priority":null,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}